reviewText: A great anime, this one has it all a great plot and some great action this one will keep you watching episode after episode not wanting to stop for a break! Make sure you have it all ready to watch. :P

The item was listed as "Used-Good" and it looks brand new. It did not have a wrapping, but I believe I was informed it would not be wrapped. My only issue was the tape on the side of the DVD left a little stain on the case other than that it looks like it has never been used!
